@{b}INSTALL:@{ub}
	Place the SamPlayerGUI program and the SamPlayerGUI.guide
	file in the sam directory as the sam_player program.


@{b}USAGE:@{ub}
	Type in some text that you want Sam_player to speak then click
	on "Say It".

	If you click on "Say It" before entering any text a default message
	will be spoken telling you to type in text or the text set in the
	tooltypes will be spoken.


@{b}TOOLTYPES:@{ub}

	Two tooltypes are currently supported.

	ENTERTALK
		If this tooltype is active then the text will be spoken
		when the "Enter" key is pressed.

	TALKSTRING
		If active sets the default text to speak if "Say It" is clicked
		before entering any text.


